column1: Lift and Drag Coefficient Data for NACA 0012 Airfoil Section

R.E. Sheldahl and P. C. Klimas, "Aerodynamic characteristics of seven symmetrical airfoil sections through 180-degree angle of attack for use in the aerodynamic analysis of vertical axis wind turbines", Sandia National Laboratories Report, SAND80-2114, 1981
*data are in 1deg angle of attack increments starting from 0 deg
